   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="1902_AS_RBH_1_00044"/>Herrn Dr Rich Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb173" type="place">Rodaun</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb40101" type="place">Liesinger Straße 2</rs></hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="1902_AS_RBH_1_00047"/><date when="1902-11-16">16. 11. 902</date></dateline></opener><p><salute>lieber Richard,</salute> die näch<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>te Zeit ko<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>
               ich kaum nach <rs ref="#pmb173" type="place">Rodaun</rs>; die Vormittage<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ind zu
               kurz, Nachmittg arbeite ich. Könnte man<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ich de<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c> nicht
               in <rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehn? Sie ko<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>en ja<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o oft herein. Das wär doch fürs er<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>te viel einfacher. Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t</p><closer>Ihr <signed>A.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
